Class RetryableDeliveryJob

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wm.app.tn.util.TNFixedData

            • permafrost.tundra.tn.delivery.RetryableDeliveryJob
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.wm.data.IData, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class RetryableDeliveryJob
extends DelegatingDeliveryJob
    A DeliveryJob which delegates to another DeliveryJob, but also supports taking into account the job's retry settings when saved after failure by using TimeUpdated to schedule the next retry at the appropriate time in the future.
    See Also:
